Introducing this amazing 2-story, 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom masterpiece in a great neighborhood. Step inside and discover an inviting open floor plan that seamlessly blends the Kitchen, Dining, and Living areas, creating the perfect space for both everyday living and entertaining. With ample natural light and modern finishes throughout, this home offers a harmonious blend of style and functionality. The spacious bedrooms provide comfort and privacy, while the 3.5 bathrooms ensure convenience for the entire family. Outside, you'll find a plenty of space to have outdoor features like a patio, garden, or deck that extends your living space. This is your opportunity to own a truly remarkable home in a desirable location. This home was built in 2017 and is in excellent condition. It is ready to move in. The house has a new Washer and Dryer pair to make regular washings a breeze!
